            h2.h3.text-center Bring along your friends and try out different flavours. &#128523; 
      div.col-lg-6.mt-5.mt-lg-0
        img.img(src="/images/coffees-donuts.jfif" alt="Coffess and Donuts") 
        <!-- photo by Anthony Anthony from https://unsplash.com/photos/auPBqoRuy_I -->
    p.marker.text-center.pt-5 "I will Come Back For More!"
    p.marker.text-center.pb-5 Our Customers
