        <!-- photo by May Lawrence from https://unsplash.com/photos/2mAZGvlgWlI -->
        div.spinning-circle.green-circle.d-flex.flex-column.justify-content-center.align-items-center
          div.text-center.fw-bolder #DONUTS
          div.text-center.fw-bolder #BAGELS
          div.text-center.fw-bolder #COFFEE
      div.col-lg-6.ps-lg-5
        h2.display-6.pb-3.pt-5 Did we mention we also make tasty bagels?
        p.fs-5 We have recently ventured into the world of bagels. We prides ourselves in our innovative menu as we here at Humphrey's Donuts are always looking to customize, improve and add new flavors to our menu. 
        p.fs-5 We also highly value our customers' wants so if there's anything you want to try, just let us know. We are always happy to give it a try!
